image.altText: A profile image of a woman with long, ice blonde hair. She has a slight smile on her face.

props.synopsis: Molly Ticehurst was allegedly murdered by her ex-boyfriend just two weeks after he faced court charged with other violent offences. A former magistrate and law expert say this shows a gap in the system that puts victims at risk.
